text: Shocked to see the YSR Congress MP obstruct a diagnostic lab (operating from a building owned by the MP) authorised by ICMR to undertake Covid-19 tests. This is a shocker at a time when the #FrontlineSoldiers are risking their lives to combat #Coronavirus. https://t.co/ZKJUMBUcv6
